metadata.name: Never Surrender #1
metadata.description:
The string is a 1 stark data structure and

everywhere it is passed there is much 

duplication of process. 3 It is a perfect vehicle 

for hiding information

Optimization hinders evolution. Everything should be 

built top-2down, except the first time. 

Simplicity does not precede complexity, 

but follows it. 4

In man-machine symbiosis, it is man who must adjust: 

The machines can't. 

Good luck. Enemy blaster
